# Implementation Plan - Intricate Test Files in `timie waste`

Create a directory named `timie waste` and populate it with several Python scripts that perform various image processing and analysis tasks.

## Proposed Changes

### [New Directory]
#### [NEW] [timie waste](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/timie_waste)

### [New Files in `timie waste`]
#### [NEW] [hog_analysis.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/timie_waste/hog_analysis.py)
 - Specialized HOG visualization with different orientations and pixels_per_cell.

#### [NEW] [glcm_analysis.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/timie_waste/glcm_analysis.py)
 - Detailed GLCM property plots (Contrast, Dissimilarity, etc. across different angles).

#### [NEW] [nlm_param_sweep.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/timie_waste/nlm_param_sweep.py)
 - Compares NLM results with varying `h` (filter strength).

#### [NEW] [clahe_demo.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/timie_waste/clahe_demo.py)
 - Demonstrates CLAHE with different clip limits and tile sizes.

#### [NEW] [edge_detection_tests.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/timie_waste/edge_detection_tests.py)
 - Compares Sobel, Canny, and Roberts edge detectors.

#### [NEW] [noise_reduction_comparison.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/timie_waste/noise_reduction_comparison.py)
 - Side-by-side comparison of Gaussian, Median, and NLM filters.

#### [NEW] [all_in_one_test.py](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/PycharmProjects/CARAT/timie_waste/all_in_one_test.py)
 - A composite script that runs all of the above on a single image.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
 - For each file, run `.venv/bin/python <filename>.py image.png` and verify it generates output images without error.

### Manual Verification
 - Check the `timie waste` directory to ensure all files are present and properly organized.
